  sentenceList:
  - <Sentence>k__BackingField: "Xin ch\xE0o nh\xE0 th\xE1m hi\u1EC3m, b\u1EA1n c\xF3
      m\u1ED9t th\u1EED th\xE1ch ngay tr\u01B0\u1EDBc m\u1EB7t \u0111\xE2y"
  - <Sentence>k__BackingField: "N\u1EBFu b\u1EA1n mu\u1ED1n c\xF3 \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c
      kho b\xE1u, b\u1EA1n h\xE3y ti\xEAu di\u1EC7t h\u1EBFt qu\xE1i v\u1EADt v\u1EDBi
      \u0111i\u1EC1u ki\u1EC7n l\xE0 s\u1ED1 h\xE0nh \u0111\u1ED9ng c\u1EE7a b\u1EA1n
      v\u1EABn c\xF2n trong gi\u1EDBi h\u1EA1n"
  - <Sentence>k__BackingField: "C\xE1c n\xFAt WASD l\xE0 \u0111\u1EC3 b\u1EA1n \u0111\u1ECBnh
      h\u01B0\u1EDBng cho k\u0129 n\u0103ng cho m\u1ED7i v\u1EADt ph\u1EA9m"
  - <Sentence>k__BackingField: "C\xF2n \u0111\u1EC3 l\u1EF1a ch\u1ECDn v\u1EADt ph\u1EA9m
      th\xEC c\xE1c n\xFAt 1-2-3-4-5 s\u1EBD gi\xFAp b\u1EA1n ch\u1ECDn"
